1. *Vreme* je odlično danas! (The weather is great today!)
2. Oni su se nadali da će *vreme* biti lepše. (They had hoped that the weather would be nicer.)
3. Želimo da provedemo više *vremena* zajedno. (We want to spend more time together.)
4. Nije preostalo puno *vremena*. (There isn't much time left.)
5. On je već potrošio svoje *vreme*. (He has already used up his time.)